  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I have _name_ attributes, for instance `<angle>`, and _description_ attributes in an HTML format.  By setting `escapeHTML` to false, attributes are recognized as HTML, but I only want the description to be HTML.\r\n\r\nFor `transformItems`, I actually stored the descriptions in a Markdown format, and tried to convert Markdown to HTML, but `escapeHTML` is not honored and items escaped.  I think `transformItems` cannot be used to control the format output.",
